  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Trade Union Co-financing Programme Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CNV Internationaal will work with the Colombian trade union movement on strengthened social dialogue at national and (sub) regional levels, with the focus on the rural areas as an instrument for the construction of sustainable peace building (SD). 
CNV Internationaal will work with the Colombian trade union CGT on improved social dialogue at company level (Drummond, Cerrejon, Prodeco and CNR) and sector level (mining) in Cesar/la Guajira, as a means to improve labour rights (C87/98) and OSH, specifically for subcontracted workers (LR).</narrative>
  </description>
